Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.56,0:01:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H7EFFFD&\pos(472,864)}4月12日 Oasis(綠洲)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.07,0:01:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為摩托車修理的比較慢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.44,0:01:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然最初我就覺得她不像好人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.86,0:01:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是那個女人就以此為借口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.64,0:01:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽還沒升起來的時候就沖過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一文錢都沒給
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.67,0:01:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開著摩托車猛沖 把橋都弄壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.25,0:01:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是我店里的客人 損失全部由我承擔了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那么豈有此理的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.93,0:01:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失陪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.29,0:01:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.51,0:01:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒錯 是Michiko Malandro吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.18,0:01:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽前臺的話說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.50,0:01:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是去Osso了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Osso？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.15,0:02:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好幾個人聽到她說 要去見Satoshi Batista
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一路很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.26,0:02:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,價格也好 味道也好 差勁到家的超級飯店
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.20,0:02:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連著光顧了3天3夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.46,0:02:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到的話只有一個詞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.81,0:02:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.13,0:02:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成長的只有頭發嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.54,0:02:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不想回去的...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.96,0:02:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那對人妖兄弟耍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.99,0:02:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.51,0:02:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被Seria那個大媽勒索 搞得身無分文
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！ 不要跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.48,0:02:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到的只是 800克滿是牛筋的牛肉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這些都過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.41,0:02:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以為我演奏一曲嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,funky風格的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色的噪音與致命的游戲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.66,0:03:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫！ 居然擅自行動！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,0:03:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我渴了 雖然是擅自行動 我要喝果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這口氣是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.56,0:03:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.01,0:03:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想聽Michiko說話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 你為什么這么生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不說我怎么能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.10,0:03:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就直說了 你是怎么想的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.96,0:03:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.92,0:03:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko 毀壞了很多東西 不付錢就跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.71,0:03:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看個屁啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作出那樣的事情 你心里是怎么想的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為Michiko的作為而流淚的人有好多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:04:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次那個修理鋪的大叔 你不該恐嚇他的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很討厭這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.99,0:04:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個嘛 是成年人之間的交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.28,0:04:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用扳手去交涉嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.00,0:04:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所做的行為都討厭 我！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你的便
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.54,0:04:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會盡快回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不許一個人在街上亂逛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:05:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\pos(206,866)\c&H1EE9FF&}愛之病
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.10,0:05:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.18,0:05:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲喲 我帶來了 奶油可可
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.48,0:05:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 你丫 怎么回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這臺狗屎機器！ 我一次都沒贏過！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你這么說...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫知道我是誰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Satoshi先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很清楚嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.23,0:05:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是Monstro Preto(黑色怪物)的老大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.73,0:05:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把老子惹毛了豈不是很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.51,0:05:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲喲 把屁眼挖挖干凈聽好 你這個土包子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我輸掉的錢和預定會贏的錢 一共2000Arca
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快去準備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則 這個家伙的Super Stick就要捅進你的屁眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了！ 我馬上去！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.13,0:05:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干的好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.30,0:05:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點事情想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到過Satoshi Batista嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.83,0:06:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說他在這個城市的什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 我不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.46,0:06:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要拔槍！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.52,0:06:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shinsuke先生...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.78,0:06:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 不要那么拘束嘛 Pogo
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.86,0:06:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什么事情！ 您居然大駕光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是上次那件事情 電話里根本談不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的Satoshi君 更本不能接受那樣的解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的有理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.02,0:06:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明沒有收到你們的孝敬錢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了一個自稱是Satoshi的人 就輕易把錢交出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也太奇怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 請不要在意 請繼續用餐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很快就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 你能讓我見見那個自稱是Satoshi的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.58,0:07:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我會去收拾他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里啊？ Pogo說的Satoshi君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.41,0:07:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等等！ Satoshi先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫 以為老子是閃閃發光的巧克力豆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能在這里做生意是托的誰的福啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Satoshi先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 別磨磨嘰嘰的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拿錢出來 還是卵蛋被踩爆 你自己挑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.31,0:08:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要聽聽卵蛋被踩爆時的美妙聲音嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢... 我付錢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.19,0:08:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 兄弟 我好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我 感動的淚流滿面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為現在幾點了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.23,0:08:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.61,0:08:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.15,0:08:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么立刻就生氣 也不聽聽我的解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看見了叫Satoshi的人 于是在后面跟蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.74,0:08:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在什么地方？ Satoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯店
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里的飯店
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Estela
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要開口 就會吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想過 我們倆還是不要在一起為好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想看見Michiko的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我承諾過 要保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什么 即使你忘記這個承諾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.27,0:09:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pogo 你說過這個飯店是四星級吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安保是零星級嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闖空門的那些混蛋 大搖大擺地就進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 你在睡覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說話 說話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別睡覺 別睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.80,0:09:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就按安排我們去最好的套房
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pogo 給我們安排保安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 費用也由你出
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\c&H03E1FD&\pos(472,1050)}四月13日 Estela飯店
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保安還沒到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.29,0:10:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說辦不到 Pogo那個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說什么 宰了他！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個禿頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.84,0:10:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話給我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.42,0:10:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是不是沒搞清楚什么叫保安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.79,0:10:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pogo那個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.51,0:10:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoshi Batista在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.24,0:10:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 平民區的總統 Satoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.05,0:10:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們早就露餡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.23,0:10:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 太冷淡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要流一身汗再回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.18,0:10:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你爽到升天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要試試 很爽的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.43,0:10:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要試試嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個輪到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.59,0:11:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么樣 我的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超絕! Jesus！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.32,0:11:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對我這如同耶穌一般的下巴你能下的了手嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.81,0:11:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 要流出來了 愛汁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我真的迷上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫 敢過來就揍你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.69,0:11:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 請再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.02,0:11:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個閃電一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心都被電焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.58,0:11:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.83,0:11:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 去叫出租車 三秒以內
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.13,0:11:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marquee!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.33,0:11:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.89,0:11:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.65,0:12:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 總統閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.96,0:12:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么 你丫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是那個黑色怪物Monstro Preto
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經包圍了飯店周圍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.15,0:12:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 Davy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 我們完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒說完呢 別掛電話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.15,0:12:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 Shinsuke
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.87,0:12:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了哦 忘記我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你丫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.28,0:12:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡小白臉的Michi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.22,0:12:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你在Vermelha大搞了一場
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來見Satoshi的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.51,0:12:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 你失望了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓那邊的總統閣下接一下電話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:12:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.36,0:12:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 Shinsuke 能讓我見見Satoshi嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:13:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 我可不會白告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不缺錢 那個要做個游戲嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫說什么 Shinsuke
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫知道我的個性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.69,0:13:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能堂堂正正地出來談談嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要 很無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.99,0:13:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 只有憑武力去問出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等 我的包
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.64,0:13:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只說自己是Satoshi 沒說是Batista
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.53,0:13:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們很強所以是黑色怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是自稱Monstro Preto而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都沒有假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是說句話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你還沒搞清你的對手是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真正的怪物 他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩游戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為交換 能放過這邊的冒牌Satoshi嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.90,0:14:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們拿的錢全部奉還
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 我絕對會贏 那時讓我見Satoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是條件
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 必須全員參加
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.22,0:14:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shinsuke
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對會贏是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話就放過那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會讓你見最想見的Satoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.88,0:14:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣沒有問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.47,0:14:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我說明一下規則
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.50,0:14:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就乘電車來見我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.16,0:14:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安地到達我這就算獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.08,0:14:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命名為“Non-stop換乘游戲”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.21,0:14:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過電車會從什么方向來 并不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便說一下 一旦搞錯了就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:14:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的人會毫不留情地射擊的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.84,0:14:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能甩掉追擊回歸正確路線 也可以饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.18,0:15:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 現在開始我要說明線路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為只說一遍 拼命記錄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.56,0:15:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別急嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.77,0:15:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 現在附近就有前往Obelisk站的電車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.64,0:15:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘這個電車 向西去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.75,0:15:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Parque Triangulo在中途換乘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.55,0:15:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面是Solao吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再往前走一點就是Santa Eatrela站...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.67,0:15:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Mercgado Central站呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.03,0:15:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里換乘前往Santa Eatrela
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Parque Triangulo縮寫成PT
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Solao 是S
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.27,0:15:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mercgado什么的 MS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Santa Estrela 是SE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后乘前往Truta站的車 再乘前往Centro站的車
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后到達Ruanova點 就這樣
