Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.07,0:15:59.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就這樣定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始 我讓飯店外面的人安靜5分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 這里是飯店Ilya Sotalia
