Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.72,0:16:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sao emar
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:16:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才來 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 為什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 SE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.57,0:17:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 搞錯了
